[Control][b]  - Move back one full screen
[Control][f]  - Move forward one full screen
[Control][d]  - Move forward 1/2 screen
[Control][u]  - Move back (up) 1/2 screen

:e file       - edit another file
:split file   - split window and load another file
ctrl-w up     - move cursor up a window
crlt-w ctrl-w - cycle cursor to another window
ctrl-w_       - maximize current window
ctrl-w=       - make all equal size
10 ctrl-w+    - increase window size by 10
:vsplit file  - vertical split
:sview file   - same as split, but readonly
:hide         - close current window
:only         - keep only this window
:ls           - show current buffers
:b 2          - open buffer #2 in this window
:vne          - open a new buffer with a vertical split
:new          - open a new buffer with a horizontal split

/pattern      - search forward for pattern
?pattern      - search backward for pattern
n             - repeat forward search
N             - repeat backward search
*             - search for word currently under cursor
g*            - search for partial word currently under cursor
ctrl-o/ctrl-i - go through jump locations
[I            - show lines with matching word under cursor 

%s/search/replace   - search whole file and replace
%s/search/replace/c - confirm each replace
